descript.abstract: UN Membership (layer) is a symbolized display presentation of the World countries 2004 and Country memberships of political organizations (table) data sets. The geographic and attribute data of World countries 2004 and the joined Country memberships of political organizations (table) are symbolized to create the layer. All features are symbolized as graduated colors based on the GA_MEMB_YR attribute in the Country memberships of political organizations (table).
